@page "/demo"

<h3>DataFilter Blazor Demo</h3>

<p>This demo showcases the Excel-like filtering capabilities in Blazor across various scenarios.</p>

<div class="list-group">
        <a href="/demo/local" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Scenario 1 — Local Filtering</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">All data is loaded locally. Filters are applied in-memory instantly.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo/attach" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Attach demo — Headless custom table</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">Keep your own HTML table markup and reuse DataFilter popups (headless mode).</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo/async" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Scenario 2 — Async Data Loading</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">Data is fetched asynchronously from an API. Results are fetched on each filter change.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo/hybrid" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Scenario 3 — Hybrid Filtering</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">Local data for row filtering; async API for distinct filter values in the popup.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo/customization" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Scenario 4 — Theme Customization</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">Toggle light/dark theme at runtime. The filter popup adapts via CSS custom properties.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo/collectionview" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-1">Scenario 6 — Collection View Integration</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-1">Filtering applied through a reactive collection state.</p>
    </a>
</div>
